name: Kentucky Fried Crypto
description: Kentucky Fried Crypto is all about giving back to the needy! A small percent tax of every transaction goes to buying buckets of tasty KFC fried chicken to be given out to the homeless and the hungry bringing some positivity in a world full of bad news! Safe & Experienced team behind it! Just launched and the marketing push is only getting started! Fighting hunger with crypto, this token aims to do good by giving back to those in need!
